              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 font-medium">学术写作</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 font-medium">创意写作</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 font-medium">用户友好性</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 font-medium">模板和工具</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐</td>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 font-medium">团队协作</td>
